FBIS4-56091 "dreeu103_y_94006" FBIS-EEU-94-103 Daily Report 27 May 1994 YUGOSLAVIA Serbia One Killed, Nine Wounded in Grenade Explosion One Killed, Nine Wounded in Grenade Explosion LD2705100194 Belgrade TANJUG in English 0944 GMT 27 May 94 LD2705100194 Belgrade TANJUG English BFN [Text] Vrnjacka Banja, May 27 (TANJUG) -- One person was killed and nine wounded when a hand granade exploded in a bus full of passengers travelling from Krusevac to Vrnjacka Banja in the central part of the Yugoslav Republic of Serbia on Thursday night [26 May]. The person suspected of having thrown the granade into the bus was arrested after the incident. Investigation is under way.
